features: Made with heavy-duty 900-denier polyester with clear ether TPU coating.
Heavy-duty TIZIP® waterproof-zipper top opening with buckle-securing over-flaps.
Removable, adjustable shoulder strap with breathable-foam pad.
Top flap secures with webbing and buckles as well as a snap for non-carrying closure.
Endcap pockets with water-resistant zippers; clear pocket inside top flap; Internal zipper pocket.
Internal foam-padded, removable insert with adjustable dividers, stow and zippered pockets.
FABRIC : 900D polyester w/ clear ether TPU + nylon webbing + perforated foam + polyester mesh.
CARE : Wipe or brush clean, store dry.
